about.summary: Library for reading and writing gif images

name: giflib
raw_recipe:
{% set version = "5.1.4" %}

package:
    name: giflib
    version: {{ version }}

source:
    fn: giflib-{{ version }}.tar.gz
    url: http://downloads.sourceforge.net/project/giflib/giflib-{{ version }}.tar.gz
    md5: 8985c9411fdb2178b89d3348da9a06b0

build:
    number: 0
    skip: True  # [win]

test:
    commands:
        - gif2rgb -h
        - gifbuild -h
        - gifclrmp -h
        - gifecho -h
        - giffix -h
        - gifinto -h
        - giftext -h
        # - conda inspect linkages giflib --prefix ${CONDA_DEFAULT_ENV}  # [linux]

about:
    home: http://giflib.sourceforge.net
    license: MIT
    summary: Library for reading and writing gif images

extra:
    recipe-maintainers:
        - ocefpaf
        - 183amir
